   <head>To the Christian Reader.</head>
   <p>
      <seg rend="decorInit">H</seg>Auing many times a desire to read some speciall Chap<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ters in the Bible, I could not so readily finde the same but by turning ouer a great Volume: now for the readier finding thereof, I haue made this briefe collection of the con<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>tents of all the Chapters conteined therein, whereby the same may be the more easily found, for the better satisfying of such, as shall haue the like desire to reade the same. And so wishing the best vse to be made thereof, I bid you Farewell.</p>
</div>
